{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a \u00a35,000 tax-free allowance for online marketplace income",
        "additional_details": "We want the UK Government to introduce a \u00a35,000 annual tax-free allowance for income earned through online marketplaces. Many people use platforms such as eBay, Vinted, Depop and Etsy to supplement their income during a period of high living costs. We believe a \u00a35,000 tax-free allowance would encourage entrepreneurship, help households manage rising costs and reduce administrative burdens for people earning modest additional income.",
        "background": "We want the UK Government to create a \u00a35,000 annual tax-free allowance for income earned through online marketplaces and side hustles, including eBay, Vinted, Depop and similar platforms.",
